Package org.sbml.jsbml.ext.arrays

Class ArraysSBasePlugin

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sbml.jsbml.AbstractTreeNode
      • org.sbml.jsbml.ext.AbstractSBasePlugin
        • org.sbml.jsbml.ext.arrays.ArraysSBasePlugin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, javax.swing.tree.TreeNode, SBasePlugin, IdManager, TreeNodeWithChangeSupport

    public class ArraysSBasePlugin
extends AbstractSBasePlugin
implements IdManager
    The ArraysSBasePlugin class extends the SBase class by adding an optional ListOfDimensions child and a single optional Index child.

    The ArraysSBasePlugin class codifies the extensions to the SBase class defined in the 'Arrays' package. These extensions allows the modeler to define one or more Dimension elements to indicate the parent SBase object is arrayed. In addition, these extensions allows the definition of one or more Index elements to reference the parent SBase that has one or more array dimensions.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Leandro Watanabe
